<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl prose prose-gray prose-sm py-12">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: April 10, 2026</p>

  <h2>What is Tikedon?</h2>
  <p>Tikedon ("we", "us", "our") is an affiliate outreach management platform for TikTok Shop sellers. We help sellers discover creators, send collaboration invitations, manage product samples, and track campaign performance through TikTok Shop's official Partner API.</p>

  <h2>What data we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Account information</strong> — email address, name, and password (hashed) when you create a Tikedon account.</li>
    <li><strong>TikTok Shop data</strong> — when you connect your TikTok Shop seller account via OAuth, we receive and store your access token, refresh token, shop name, and shop identifier. Tokens are encrypted at rest.</li>
    <li><strong>Creator data</strong> — publicly available creator profile information (handle, follower count, GMV, categories) retrieved through TikTok Shop's official API.</li>
    <li><strong>Campaign and invite data</strong> — messages you compose, campaigns you create, invites sent, sample tracking, and Spark Ads codes you enter.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — pages visited, features used, AI call logs (token counts for cost tracking).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How we use your data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To provide the Tikedon service — searching creators, sending invites, managing samples.</li>
    <li>To authenticate your TikTok Shop connection and make API calls on your behalf.</li>
    <li>To run AI-powered message generation and moderation (via Anthropic's Claude API).</li>
    <li>To track your AI usage costs.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How we store and protect data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>All data is stored in a PostgreSQL database hosted on US-based servers.</li>
    <li>TikTok OAuth tokens are <strong>encrypted at rest</strong> using Rails 8 ActiveRecord encryption.</li>
    <li>Passwords are hashed with bcrypt and never stored in plaintext.</li>
    <li>HTTPS is enforced for all connections.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>TikTok Shop Partner API</strong> — we send API requests on your behalf using your authorized tokens. TikTok's privacy policy applies to data on their platform.</li>
    <li><strong>Anthropic Claude API</strong> — message text is sent to Claude for moderation and generation. Anthropic's data usage policy applies. We do not send personal identifying information to Claude beyond the message content itself.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data sharing</h2>
  <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell your data. We share data only with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>TikTok — via their API, as authorized by you through OAuth.</li>
    <li>Anthropic — message content for AI processing.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data retention</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Account data is retained while your account is active.</li>
    <li>TikTok tokens are deleted when you disconnect your shop.</li>
    <li>Campaign and invite history is retained for your records even after disconnecting.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Disconnect your TikTok Shop at any time (deletes tokens).</li>
    <li>Request deletion of your account and all associated data by contacting us.</li>
    <li>Export your data on request.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>For privacy questions, contact us at <strong>privacy@tikedon.com</strong>.</p>
</div>
